 />\n<br />\n$ mra go fuck Microsoft<br />\nfuc!@#$%^&amp;k Microsoft<br />\n<br />\n你話幾盞鬼呢! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cfe4eeb51d558a280d085ca031e0afa79a8fc6b","tid":219212,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:42:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇game推介？</blockquote><br />\nSteam 有好多 Linux game <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝提醒一陣 John <br />\n<br />\n不過唔知流唔流暢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e884fd33daad2016df0ebdf2c40d7a7ef2fe97","tid":219212,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:49:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇game推介？</blockquote><br />\nSteam 有好多 Linux game <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝提醒一陣 John <br />\n<br />\n不過唔知流唔流暢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n留名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf0913d4d5e190ae6b6ebef3a35feadc850f27b","tid":219212,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:49:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Mr a識條鐵咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你先唔識嘢! 如果有隻Linux distro 係build in咗Mr.A AI utility program嘅話, 我會即john囉!<br />\ne.g. <br />\n$ mra<br />\nJohn Linux!<br />\n<br />\n$ mra go fuck Microsoft<br />\nfuc!@#$%^&amp;k Microsoft<br />\n<br />\n你話幾盞鬼呢! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f5cdfbf4366e3fa43b0d19996aadf639037142","tid":219212,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:52:51.000Z","msg":"如果樓主討厭用vim, emacs嗰啲, 又要輕ken嘅text editor for programmers and web developers嘅話, 可以試下john Bluefish.  <br />\n<a href=\"http://bluefish.openoffice.nl/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbluefish.openoffice.nl%2Findex.html&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=79294245\" target=\"_blank\">http://bluefish.openoffice.nl/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n再唔係可以john Notepadqq, 功能同Windows上嘅Notepad++大致相同!<br />\n<a href=\"http://notepadqq.altervista.org/wp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnotepadqq.altervista.org%2Fwp%2F&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=b0d814fb\" target=\"_blank\">http://notepadqq.altervista.org/wp/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905025410910352933f269ce2afc9f147397e0c7","tid":219212,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:57:44.000Z","msg":"其實最想要係下邊嘅嘢各 Linux 高手請畀啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暫時行住 virtual box 先覺得好用先 dual boot<br />\n冇計返工同打機都係有 Mac and PC 比較方便<br />\n<br />\nRemote Desktop 類似 VNC 係咪用 X11 client 之類？定我 out 咗好耐？<br />\n<br />\nCisco VPN 駁返公司 我遲啲查下有冇 client<br />\n<br />\nIDE 之前有巴打有提議未得閑裝 仲有乜好嘅 ide 請𧶽教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nR python Hadoop spark etc. GitHub etc<br />\n間唔中寫下 web 如 js php CSS etc. 主要都係用 WordPress 所以好少要喺 desktop 寫<br />\n係咪學 git 先？ 定SVN? <br />\n或者會裝 monodevelop 玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSublime text 好似都有 Linux 版？<br />\n<br />\nBrowser 裝咗 opera. Cli 打句嘢就裝到好方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n類似 Winmerge 嘅嘢？好似話 cli 其實好易，但有冇啲有 GUI?<br />\n如果 IDE 做到就唔使了<br />\n<br />\nMySQL admin GUI 工作需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果有其他嘢方便寫 program 同 manage Linux 請介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nopenSUSE leap 42.2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e03daa12bb9182b1773b0079cc9388a077c0c550","tid":219212,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:00:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇game推介？</blockquote><br />\nSteam 有好多 Linux game <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝提醒一陣 John <br />\n<br />\n不過唔知流唔流暢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n留名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n行 VM 唔會寄予厚望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我鍾意玩簡單 game 多<br />\n好多 indie games 都有 Linux 版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇下 mini metro human resource machine 之類有冇得玩先<br />\n<br />\n之後報告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}